                <h3 class="timeline-title">C# (.NET) / Java Developer</h3>
                <p class="timeline-meta">Ankama &mdash; Roubaix, France &nbsp;|&nbsp; November 2022 – August 2025</p>
                <p class="timeline-text">
                    I joined Ankama as part of the technical porting of the video game Dofus from flash technology to the Unity game engine.
                    In a team of 10 Front-end developpers, I developped the new features, fixed bugs and optimized the performance of the game.
                    I also was in charge of the development of the new UIs and assured code quality through numeruous code reviews.
                </p>
                <div class="tags">
                    <span class="tag tag-blue">Unity</span>
                    <span class="tag">C# (.NET)</span>
                    <span class="tag tag-teal">Java</span>
                    <span class="tag tag-orange">SQL</span>
