                    <span class="tag tag-light">Youtrack</span>
                    <span class="tag tag-sage">Gitlab</span>
                    <span class="tag tag-blue">UI / UX</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <h3 class="timeline-title">Support Engineer</h3>
                <p class="timeline-meta">Decathlon &mdash; Croix, France &nbsp;|&nbsp; September 2021 – September 2022</p>
                <p class="timeline-text">
                    Integrated in the core of the supply chain, in the production department team, I implemented monitoring of the databases and applications used by the production countries.
                    I also set up visualizations of numerous KPIs according to the needs of the different teams.
                    I facilitated some agile ceremonies. I also volunteered with the "Sustainable Value Chain for Industry" group to implement a system for
                    monitoring consumption metrics for our software.
                </p>
                <div class="tags">
                    <span class="tag tag-blue">Splunk</span>
                    <span class="tag">SQL</span>
                    <span class="tag tag-teal">Java</span>
                    <span class="tag tag-orange">PostgreSQL</span>
                    <span class="tag tag-red">Oracle</span>
