                    <span class="tag tag-sage">Scrum</span>
                    <span class="tag tag-blue">ITIL</span>
                    <span class="tag">SRE (System Reliability Engineering)</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <h3 class="timeline-title">C# Developper</h3>
                <p class="timeline-meta">INRIA &mdash; Villeneuve d'Ascq, France &nbsp;|&nbsp; April 2021 – August 2021</p>
                <p class="timeline-text">
                    I joined INRIA to support the technical development of a doctoral student's thesis, which focused on 
                    "Interaction Techniques for Object Selection and Facial Expression Control in Virtual Reality." 
                    We were supervised by two professors. My role was to gamify the experience and set up a VR meeting scene where users could, 
                    among other things, project documents, interact with objects, and so on all across the network.
                </p>
